	(24,2,'2014-07-29 06:20:59','2014-07-29 06:20:59','<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-465 \" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\" alt=\"15408114854_df39085885_z\" width=\"401\" height=\"535\" /></a></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is one of two houses located in the California Bay Area affiliated with Ronald McDonald House Charities of the Bay Area and Ronald McDonald House Charities (Global).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is, however, a separate 501(c)(3) non-profit corporation. McDonald\'s is our largest corporate donor and a portion of the annual operating costs for each Ronald McDonald House in San Francisco is graciously funded by local McDonald\'s restaurants and owner/operators. The remainder of our annual operating income, about 85-90%, comes from the generosity of individuals, corporate donors and some small foundation grants.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">McDonald’s involvement extends beyond monetary support:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Franchisees partner with the House for promotional and fundraising events.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> • Several owner/operators serve on our Advisory Council.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although McDonald’s is our largest corporate donor, no company can solely fund our programs and our projected growth. We need the support of the entire community and greatly value any support you can afford to the Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco, whether it’s through cash donations, your time, your talents, spreading the word as an ambassador, or fundraising efforts.</span>','Our Relationship with McDonald\'s','','publish','closed','closed','','our-relationship-with-mcdonalds','','','2015-01-16 13:38:10','2015-01-16 21:38:10','',18,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com?page_id=24',3,'page','',0),
