	(56,1,'2014-07-29 06:27:07','2014-07-29 06:27:07','<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/2011-ACN-Conference-006.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-1465\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/2011-ACN-Conference-006-1024x770.jpg\" alt=\"2011 ACN Conference 006\" width=\"614\" height=\"462\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">It’s back! ACN is a three-day convention that takes place at the SAP center in San Jose. Last year, we were able to raise over $80,000 and this year we are hoping to do more! This is an event when we really count on you, our wonderful friends and volunteers, to turn up in droves while people LITERALLY throw money at us!</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #780005;\">ACN Fundraiser at HP Pavilion, San Jose</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-single\">\r\n<div class=\"page-restrict-output\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #780005;\">IT’S BACK!!!</h1>\r\n<a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/IMG_7948.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-1543\" title=\"IMG_7948\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/IMG_7948-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"614\" height=\"461\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dear Friends- The Wild &amp; Crazy volunteer experience of ACN is back!  Join us for the one of our House’s most talked-about and popular volunteer events.  We’ve done it four times and volunteers who have been part of it can’t wait to get the news it’s “on” again.  We can raise  MAJOR BUCKS for our House and the Stanford House to split –as  much as $80,000 has been raised! WHAT IT TAKES is LOTS AND LOTS OF VOLUNTEERS.  And it’s a  challenge to recruit enough for a summer month of June.  In short,  this is a moment when the House really needs you and would be deeply grateful for your donation of your time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Along with our “Be our Guest” photo booth we will be including a <i>“Kids Zone” </i>for the ACN families to enjoy! During this time of expansion we need all hands on deck. Please come show your support and help us grow!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">What <b><i>is</i></b> this event?</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">A  convention of people who sell telecommunications products for a company called “ACN.”  Our role as volunteers: to walk around the concourse of the SAP Center interacting with fun and generous attendees who literally (we mean it) throw money at us.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">It’s an amazing experience, which many describe as their wildest volunteer experience ever.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Where:                    SAP Center in San Jose</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dates:                      June 20th, 21st and 22nd</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Volunteer Shifts:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> Friday </strong>      9:00am – 2:30pm</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>6/20/14</strong>    2:00pm – 6:30pm</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Saturday</strong>   6:30 am – 11:00 am</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> 6/21/14</strong>    10:30am – 3:00 pm</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">2:30 pm – 6:45 pm</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> Sunday</strong>      6:30 am – 11:00 am</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong> 6/22/14</strong>    10:30am – 2:30 pm</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b><i>**Sign up for more than one shift if you can.**</i></b></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b><i>**We need 15 volunteers minimum for each shift**</i></b></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Join us AND/OR please recruit outgoing friends, family and co-workers!!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Families can volunteer together; parents are required to keep their children with them at all times. Please respond to Melinda Prieto, Volunteer Coordinator at <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"mailto:melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org\" target=\"_blank\">melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a> or <a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"tel:415.673.0891\" target=\"_blank\">415.673.0891</a>.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Community Fundraisers','','publish','open','closed','','community-fundraisers','','','2014-11-24 17:32:12','2014-11-24 17:32:12','',274,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com?page_id=56',3,'page','',0),
