	(123,3,'2014-08-01 21:13:35','2014-08-01 21:13:35','<div class=\"title\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<h1 style=\"color: #780005;\">2014 Home Away From Home Gala</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-single\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"page-restrict-output\">\r\n\r\n<a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/RMHSF_2014Gala_WebsiteGraphic.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-1831\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/RMHSF_2014Gala_WebsiteGraphic.jpg\" alt=\"RMHSF_2014Gala_WebsiteGraphic\" width=\"819\" height=\"255\" /></a>\r\n\r\nJoin us for the 2014 Home Away From Home Gala, benefiting the children and families of Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco.\r\n\r\n2014 Home Away From Home Gala\r\nFriday, October 17th, 2014\r\nFour Seasons Hotel, San Francisco\r\nReception &amp; Silent Auction, 6:30 – 7:45pm\r\nDinner, Live Auction &amp; Entertainment, 7:45pm – Midnight\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://ronaldhouse-sf.ejoinme.org/MyEvents/Home/Registration/tabid/535283/Default.aspx\">Purchase sponsorships and tickets online </a></strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2014 Home Away From Home Gala','','inherit','open','open','','54-revision-v1','','','2014-08-01 21:13:35','2014-08-01 21:13:35','',54,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/?p=123',0,'revision','',0),
	(124,3,'2014-08-01 21:15:12','2014-08-01 21:15:12','<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Our Challenge</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">As San Francisco’s medical facilities continue to expand their specialized pediatric care services, particularly at the new UCSF Benioff Children’s Hospital at Mission Bay, a growing number of families continue to seek the services of the Ronald McDonald House. However, a major roadblock threatens our ability to provide a home-away-from-home: Ronald McDonald House is forced to turn away families for lack of space.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Our Solution</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Leaders of the Ronald McDonald House have launched “Hearts &amp; Hands,” a comprehensive fundraising campaign enabling Ronald McDonald House to triple the number of families with critically ill children served. Through the “Hearts &amp; Hands Campaign,” RMH-SF will open a second House <em>inside</em> UCSF Benioff Children’s Hospital at Mission Bay, complete needed upgrades of the current House on Scott Street, support the growth of our beloved hospital-based family programs, and cover the costs of operating two facilities.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Your generosity keeps families together at this difficult time and lightens their financial load. Family members draw comfort and hope from Ronald McDonald House’s caring community of volunteers, staff, and fellow families coping with the critical illness of their child. They are awed by the realization that wonderful supporters of the House are standing beside them and helping them through this challenging time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Plans for a Second House</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"New SF Ronald McDonald House\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org/test/graphics/Content/NewHouse.png\" alt=\"New SF Ronald McDonald House\" width=\"800\" height=\"625\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">How to Help</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">To learn more about our future plans and how you can get involved, please contact us at:</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco\r\n1640 Scott Street\r\nSan Francisco, CA 94115\r\nPhone: (415) 673-0891\r\nFax: (415) 673-1335\r\n<a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">info@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a></p>','Hearts & Hands Campaign','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision-v1','','','2014-08-01 21:15:12','2014-08-01 21:15:12','',41,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/?p=124',0,'revision','',0),
	(125,3,'2014-08-01 21:17:32','2014-08-01 21:17:32','Generous donations of time and money allow us to continue to provide a comfortable home-away-from-home for the families who need our services. There are many ways you can help, and your kindness is always appreciated.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Make a <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://ronaldhouse-sf.ejoinme.org/MyPages/DonationPage/tabid/229897/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">financial contribution</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>Donate stock or estate gifts.</li>\r\n	<li>Sponsor our annual Gala and/or Golf Tournament.</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer your time.</li>\r\n	<li>Invite us to do a presentation about the Ronald McDonald House for your organization or club.</li>\r\n	<li>Contribute items from our <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/how-you-can-help/wish-list/\">wishlist</a>.</li>\r\n	<li><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.donatingiseasy.org/donate-car-any-charity.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Donate a vehicle</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur Federal EIN is 94-2951627. For additional information, email us at <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">info@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Volulnteers Cleaning\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/test/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/Volulnteers-Cleaning.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"824\" height=\"620\" />','Donate','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision-v1','','','2014-08-01 21:17:32','2014-08-01 21:17:32','',35,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/?p=125',0,'revision','',0),
