ganization than the Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco. It was a true pleasure working with them to create something special.  In order to make the website truly usable, users need to be able to access and use the website from their mobile devices. With responsive design technology, the website is automatically sized and scaled to each mobile device and tablet. People are increasingly viewing the Internet on their phones and tablets; so it is important that users be able view and utilize the site as it was intended to be.  We\'re hoping that by furthering the online presence, more great things will come.”\r\n- Matt Santos, COO of AG Design Group.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/santos.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-188\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/santos-300x240.jpg\" alt=\"santos\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" /></a>','Website Credits','','inherit','open','open','','186-revision-v1','','','2014-08-05 08:41:21','2014-08-05 08:41:21','',186,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/?p=198',0,'revision','',0),
