	(326,4,'2014-11-21 23:28:30','2014-11-21 23:28:30','<h2>Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Hosts 25th Anniversary Gala; Exceeds Fundraising Goals</h2>\r\n<em>October 30, 2014 -</em> The House hosted its annual <em>Home Away From Home</em> gala on October 17th at the Four Seasons in San Francisco and, through the generosity of new and longtime supporters, was able to raise nearly $325,000–exceeding goals for the event and setting a new fundraising record for the House. Of the funds raised, $86,000 came from the <em>Fill-A-Heart</em> individual donation portion of the live auction.\r\n\r\nAnother first for the House was achieved when Senator Mark Leno presented a resolution to honor the House’s 25 years of service to families with critically ill children. Masters of Ceremony Cheryl Jennings and Mike Nicco added a lively energy to the program and highlighted personal stories from families who have stayed at the House. The evening ended with dinner and a dance floor jam-packed thanks to music by the ever-popular Pride &amp; Joy.\r\n\r\nTo see the photo gallery, click on the photo below.','2014 HOME AWAY FROM HOME GALA','','inherit','open','open','','82-revision-v1','','','2014-11-21 23:28:30','2014-11-21 23:28:30','',82,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/82-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(327,5,'2015-01-16 13:05:29','2015-01-16 21:05:29','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco depends on the generosity of our volunteer community to provide time, talent and all types of support.  “In-kind” donations, contributions of materials, goods and services, allow us to provide for families in a “home away from home” environment.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>We are always seeking a variety of new and unused household goods such as:</strong></p>\n\n<div style=\"color: #000000;\">\n<ul>\n	<li>Paper towels</li>\n	<li>Arm and Hammer Dermatologist tested No Scent Laundry Detergent</li>\n	<li>Ajax Grapefruit Dish Soap</li>\n	<li>Cascade Complete</li>\n	<li>Shampoo</li>\n	<li>Conditioner</li>\n	<li>Body Wash (dermatologist tested/non allergenic)</li>\n	<li>Lysol Disinfecting Wipes Ocean Fresh Scent (80 wipes we utilize in 1 week)</li>\n	<li>Simple Green Pro 3</li>\n	<li>Scrubbing Bubbles</li>\n	<li>Windex</li>\n	<li>Individual snacks (chips, cookies, fruit snacks, granola bars, pudding)</li>\n	<li>White bath &amp; hand towels &amp; washcloths</li>\n	<li>Queen size white sheets &amp; pillowcases</li>\n	<li>Drawstring garbage bags (kitchen &amp; 33-gallon)</li>\n	<li>Gift cards such as Target, Smart &amp; Final, Safeway, Costco, Chevron, Subway</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>Please visit our Amazon wishlist for our current needs:</strong>\n\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Holiday Wish List\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/3ABUAKBDIV4M1/ref=topnav_lists_1\" target=\"_blank\">2014 Holiday Wishlist!</a></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/101NPRNN8CD93/ref=cm_sw_su_w\" target=\"_blank\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist</a></span>\n\n<em>Any questions, suggestions or concerns please contact </em><a href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">info</a><a href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\">@ronaldhouse-sf.org</span></a>.\n\nItems can be dropped off at the House at 1640 Scott Street, San Francisco, CA 94115.\nTo arrange a drop-off date and time please call us at (415) 673-0891.\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Thank you for your support!</h2>\n</div>','Our Wish List','','inherit','open','open','','45-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-16 13:05:29','2015-01-16 21:05:29','',45,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/45-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
