	(386,4,'2014-12-09 16:34:45','2014-12-10 00:34:45','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">The kitchen is the heart of every home and we don’t want to skip a beat. Our kitchen provides a space where families not only find nourishment but a space where they find they are not alone.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">After spending hours upon hours in the hospital with an ill child, one may lack the energy and resources to take care of themselves. This is where incredible volunteers- like you, can make a huge difference by providing a family style meal.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">As a Family Meal Volunteer, you will have the flexibility to volunteer as little or often as possible. This is a great project for individuals that cannot commit for long periods of time but appreciate the value of sharing a moment.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Requirements:</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">*We ask for no more than six people in your group as the kitchen can get crowded.*</p>\n\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>Dinners are seven days a week, and are served at 7 p.m. Groups should plan to arrive by 6:00pm. Depending on your menu, you may want to arrange with our office for an earlier arrival. (Our strongest need is for weekday meals).</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>Breakfasts are now also served seven days a week. Breakfast is served at 9:30 a.m. Monday through Friday , you can arrive at the House anytime after 8:30am. On Saturdays and Sundays you can arrive as early as 8:00am.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>On the calendar, if a date has “breakfast group” or “dinner group” written on it, that means that the time slot for that date has already been filled. Please choose a day that does not already have the meal of your choice filled in.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>Ronald McDonald House provides all kitchen cookware, utensils and beverages. You will need to provide ingredients for your meal. (Basics provided: seasonings, flour, oils, etc.) If possible, please <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"mailto:melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">email</a> us a copy of the menu in advance so we can let the families know what delicious meal will be prepared.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>Meals should serve 15-20, and include a vegetarian component. Your group is encouraged to join the families for the meal. Not all families are at the House for the 7 p.m. dinnertime as they often stay at the hospital until late evening, but the leftovers are very much appreciated by late returns!</li>\n</ul>\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\n	<li>Please clean-up following your dinner (load dishwasher, wipe tables, etc.).</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">If you would like to prepare a meal for our families, please fill out our <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://www.volgistics.com/ex/portal.dll/ap?AP=1916799279\" target=\"_blank\">Group Volunteer Application</a>.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?height=600&amp;wkst=1&amp;bgcolor=%23ffcc99&amp;src=0nk2q7od4gua0dptk097movovs%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;color=%232952A3&amp;ctz=America%2FLos_Angeles\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>','Family Meals','','inherit','open','open','','130-autosave-v1','','','2014-12-09 16:34:45','2014-12-10 00:34:45','',130,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/130-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(387,4,'2014-12-09 16:43:44','2014-12-10 00:43:44','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">The kitchen is the heart of every home and we don’t want to skip a beat. Our kitchen provides a space where families not only find nourishment but a space where they find they are not alone.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">After spending hours upon hours in the hospital with an ill child, one may lack the energy and resources to take care of themselves. This is where incredible volunteers- like you, can make a huge difference by providing a family style meal.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">As a Family Meal Volunteer, you will have the flexibility to volunteer as little or often as possible. This is a great project for individuals that cannot commit for long periods of time but appreciate the value of sharing a moment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Requirements:</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">*We ask for no more than six people in your group as the kitchen can get crowded.*</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Dinners are seven days a week, and are served at 7 p.m. Groups should plan to arrive by 6:00pm. Depending on your menu, you may want to arrange with our office for an earlier arrival. (Our strongest need is for weekday meals).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Breakfasts are now also served seven days a week. Breakfast is served at 9:30 a.m. Monday through Friday , you can arrive at the House anytime after 8:30am. On Saturdays and Sundays you can arrive as early as 8:00am.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>On the calendar, if a date has “breakfast group” or “dinner group” written on it, that means that the time slot for that date has already been filled. Please choose a day that does not already have the meal of your choice filled in.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Ronald McDonald House provides all kitchen cookware, utensils and beverages. You will need to provide ingredients for your meal. (Basics provided: seasonings, flour, oils, etc.) If possible, please <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"mailto:melinda@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">email</a> us a copy of the menu in advance so we can let the families know what delicious meal will be prepared.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Meals should serve 15-20, and include a vegetarian component. Your group is encouraged to join the families for the meal. Not all families are at the House for the 7 p.m. dinnertime as they often stay at the hospital until late evening, but the leftovers are very much appreciated by late returns!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Please clean-up following your dinner (load dishwasher, wipe tables, etc.).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">If you would like to prepare a meal for our families, please fill out our <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://www.volgistics.com/ex/portal.dll/ap?AP=1916799279\" target=\"_blank\">Group Volunteer Application</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?height=600&amp;wkst=1&amp;bgcolor=%23ffcc99&amp;src=0nk2q7od4gua0dptk097movovs%40group.calendar.google.com&amp;color=%232952A3&amp;ctz=America%2FLos_Angeles\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>','Family Meals','','inherit','open','open','','130-revision-v1','','','2014-12-09 16:43:44','2014-12-10 00:43:44','',130,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/130-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
