	(506,5,'2015-01-14 12:57:27','2015-01-14 20:57:27','<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Welcome to the Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/16029552012_dae5dc3762_z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-494 size-medium\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/16029552012_dae5dc3762_z-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"16029552012_dae5dc3762_z\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco, Inc. (RMH-SF) provides a safe haven for critically ill children and their families.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our caring staff and volunteers have been helping families since opening our doors in 1989. The RMH-SF provides temporary housing, home-cooked meals and supportive services for families while their children receive specialized treatment in a San Francisco hospital. The House offers a home-like environment where family members find comfort through supportive staff, volunteers and other families in similar situations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Families are stronger when they are together, and their presence helps a sick child heal faster and cope better. While we cannot make medicine taste better or take away painful treatments, we can help lessen the burden and ensure families have the stability and resources to get and keep their child healthy and happy. Last year, 137 families found respite at our House for a combined total of 3,215 guest night stays, all because of the love and generous donations of our donors and volunteers.</p>','Mission','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-v1','','','2015-01-14 12:57:27','2015-01-14 20:57:27','',14,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(507,5,'2015-01-14 12:59:32','2015-01-14 20:59:32','<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is one of two houses located in the California Bay Area affiliated with Ronald McDonald House Charities of the Bay Area and Ronald McDonald House Charities (Global).</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-465 \" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\" alt=\"15408114854_df39085885_z\" width=\"401\" height=\"535\" /></a></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is, however, a separate 501(c)(3) non-profit corporation. McDonald\'s is our largest corporate donor and a portion of the annual operating costs for each Ronald McDonald House in San Francisco is graciously funded by local McDonald\'s restaurants and owner/operators. The remainder of our annual operating income, about 85-90%, comes from the generosity of individuals, corporate donors and some small foundation grants.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">McDonald’s involvement extends beyond monetary support:</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Franchisees partner with the House for promotional and fundraising events.</span>\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> • McDonald\'s vendors, such as Martin Brower and Coca-Cola, are also donors to the House.</span>\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> • Several owner/operators serve on our Advisory Council.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although McDonald’s is our largest corporate donor, no company can solely fund our programs and our projected growth. We need the support of the entire community and greatly value any support you can afford to the Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco, whether it’s through cash donations, your time, your talents, spreading the word as an ambassador, or fundraising efforts.</span>','Our Relationship with McDonald\'s','','inherit','open','open','','24-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-14 12:59:32','2015-01-14 20:59:32','',24,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/24-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
