	(555,5,'2015-01-16 12:44:25','2015-01-16 20:44:25','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Join us in fulfilling our mission! We have an array of important positions, for both individuals and groups. Volunteers are strong partners in the work we do. We welcome corporate teams, office groups, schools, service organizations, alumni groups, associations, families, fraternities, sororities and religious organizations. You are an essential part of making our house a home.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">We understand that helpful hearts have busy calendars. Therefore, we have redesigned our volunteer program to work within your schedule.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><em> **Attending a Volunteer Informational Session does not guarantee volunteer placement. Please complete the application below to register.**</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Current Volunteer Opportunities</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/scott.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-394\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/scott-300x228.png\" alt=\"scott\" width=\"233\" height=\"177\" /></a>      <a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Mission.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-395\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Mission-300x205.png\" alt=\"Mission\" width=\"244\" height=\"167\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><strong>  Volunteer at the Scott Street House              Volunteer at the Mission Bay House</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/cbp.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-396\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/cbp.png\" alt=\"cbp\" width=\"229\" height=\"171\" /></a>       <a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/event.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-397\" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/event-300x228.jpg\" alt=\"event\" width=\"234\" height=\"178\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000; text-align: center;\"><strong>  Volunteer in the hospital                                     Host a Fundraising Event</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color: #000000; text-align: left; padding-left: 90px;\"> Thank you for your interest in volunteering at The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco!</div>','Volunteer','','inherit','open','open','','43-revision-v1','','','2015-01-16 12:44:25','2015-01-16 20:44:25','',43,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/43-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(556,5,'2015-01-16 13:05:38','2015-01-16 21:05:38','<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco depends on the generosity of our volunteer community to provide time, talent and all types of support.  “In-kind” donations, contributions of materials, goods and services, allow us to provide for families in a “home away from home” environment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>We are always seeking a variety of new and unused household goods such as:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Paper towels</li>\r\n	<li>Arm and Hammer Dermatologist tested No Scent Laundry Detergent</li>\r\n	<li>Ajax Grapefruit Dish Soap</li>\r\n	<li>Cascade Complete</li>\r\n	<li>Shampoo</li>\r\n	<li>Conditioner</li>\r\n	<li>Body Wash (dermatologist tested/non allergenic)</li>\r\n	<li>Lysol Disinfecting Wipes Ocean Fresh Scent (80 wipes we utilize in 1 week)</li>\r\n	<li>Simple Green Pro 3</li>\r\n	<li>Scrubbing Bubbles</li>\r\n	<li>Windex</li>\r\n	<li>Individual snacks (chips, cookies, fruit snacks, granola bars, pudding)</li>\r\n	<li>White bath &amp; hand towels &amp; washcloths</li>\r\n	<li>Queen size white sheets &amp; pillowcases</li>\r\n	<li>Drawstring garbage bags (kitchen &amp; 33-gallon)</li>\r\n	<li>Gift cards such as Target, Smart &amp; Final, Safeway, Costco, Chevron, Subway</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Please visit our Amazon wishlist for our current needs:</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Holiday Wish List\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/3ABUAKBDIV4M1/ref=topnav_lists_1\" target=\"_blank\">2014 Holiday Wishlist!</a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"><a style=\"color: #800000;\" title=\"Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/registry/wishlist/101NPRNN8CD93/ref=cm_sw_su_w\" target=\"_blank\">Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco Wishlist</a></span>\r\n\r\n<em>Any questions, suggestions or concerns please contact </em><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><a style=\"color: #993300;\" href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">info</a><a style=\"color: #993300;\" href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a></span>.\r\n\r\nItems can be dropped off at the House at 1640 Scott Street, San Francisco, CA 94115.\r\nTo arrange a drop-off date and time please call us at (415) 673-0891.\r\n<h2 style=\"color: #227896;\">Thank you for your support!</h2>\r\n</div>','Our Wish List','','inherit','open','open','','45-revision-v1','','','2015-01-16 13:05:38','2015-01-16 21:05:38','',45,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/45-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(557,5,'2015-01-16 13:38:10','2015-01-16 21:38:10','<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-465 \" src=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/15408114854_df39085885_z.jpg\" alt=\"15408114854_df39085885_z\" width=\"401\" height=\"535\" /></a></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is one of two houses located in the California Bay Area affiliated with Ronald McDonald House Charities of the Bay Area and Ronald McDonald House Charities (Global).</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco is, however, a separate 501(c)(3) non-profit corporation. McDonald\'s is our largest corporate donor and a portion of the annual operating costs for each Ronald McDonald House in San Francisco is graciously funded by local McDonald\'s restaurants and owner/operators. The remainder of our annual operating income, about 85-90%, comes from the generosity of individuals, corporate donors and some small foundation grants.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">McDonald’s involvement extends beyond monetary support:</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">• Franchisees partner with the House for promotional and fundraising events.</span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> • Several owner/operators serve on our Advisory Council.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although McDonald’s is our largest corporate donor, no company can solely fund our programs and our projected growth. We need the support of the entire community and greatly value any support you can afford to the Ronald McDonald House of San Francisco, whether it’s through cash donations, your time, your talents, spreading the word as an ambassador, or fundraising efforts.</span>','Our Relationship with McDonald\'s','','inherit','open','open','','24-revision-v1','','','2015-01-16 13:38:10','2015-01-16 21:38:10','',24,'http://ronaldhouse-sf.org.97.69-195-223.groveurl.com/24-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
